node.text: Mommy and Daddy took us the new WTC Cortlandt Street Subway Station in NYC. It was demolished on Sept 11, and just opened after 17 years. 🌹 #wtccortlandt #oneworldtradecenter #pupsofinstagram #pup #dogsofinstagram #dogs #cute #cutenessoverload #cuties #chihuahua #chihuahuasofinstagram
